            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"><td class="py-1">Week 3-4</td><td>50% off</td><td>$50</td><td>Most balanced value/selection point</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"><td class="py-1">Week 5-6</td><td>60-70% off</td><td>$30-$40</td><td>Size/color gaps appear — patient shoppers win</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"><td class="py-1">Week 7-8</td><td>75% off</td><td>$25</td><td>"Final markdown" sticker often appears</td></tr>
